        <TD bgcolor='dimgray' valign='top'><font color='white' face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica' size='2'>I did my dagger at 44. First imprecator was easy, spawned after 2 PHs and dropped nice robe of dalnir with dagger piece  =) Breaking his room was easy, I parked my pet right outside a hole in a wall from drop down room, and single pulled things out for augmented pet to kill. </P><P>Church was tricky. Key was to make sure that roamer in a hall where one way door is, is not aggro. Have FD memmed, wait till that sperm of death or goo shows up, and just sit <img src=icon_smile.gif border=0 align=middle>  If it proceeds to beat the poop out of you, feign, then stand up, root and kill. Remember, wandering mobs NEVER forget FD. If you want them to forget you, you have to  /q out and log back in. Once you got non aggro spawn there, set up your pet in that big room before one way door, dont set up in that small room closer to church. Once you get attacked, pet will rush in and train you.  Usually non aggro sperms and goos are kept alive by everyone who passes by. They will still scowl, but will ignore you. </P><P>Pull things out with darkness, and rush back to pet. Root the mob once at pet, and med. Pet will rip it to shreds. Continue pulling them one by one. Casters (channeler and Evoker) can do some decent damage, get lifetap ready. Shaman mobs will try to slow your pet, and they might heal mobs through walls, watch out. </P><P>Lab area breakin for me was pretty much killing every mob on the way there from entrance to that place.  Set up where water meets ground, park pet there, clean out all kly. Weird pathing bug will make all mobs appear to be stuck at first doorway you will see, and for some reason they can still hurt you, even non casters. Pet will aggro, cause a gigantic train, watch out. after you cleared out up to lab, go inside lab, park pet as far as you can away from the door and wait. That room has 2 spawns, either can be imprecator. Dont let pet get out of the door. If you let him, FEIGN right away, because you WILL die if you dont feign.</P><P>Good luck on this.</P><P>Flatin Shadowmaster<BR>Sexiest Gnome Heretic ever<BR>Proud member of L`Malla<BR>Druzzil Ro server</font></td>
